<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Architect Strategic Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #00ff00;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .dashboard {
            border: 1px solid #ffd700;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo-section img { width: 100px; filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px gold); margin-bottom: 10px; }

        .stat-card {
            background: #111;
            border: 1px solid #222;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 0.85rem; margin: 5px 0; }
        .gold { color: #ffd700; font-weight: bold; }
        .highlight { color: #fff; font-size: 1.1rem; }

        .monthly-badge {
            background: #ffd700;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 0.6rem;
            color: #444;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="dashboard">
        <div class="logo-section">
            <img src="1000006643.png" alt="AA Logo">
            <h3 style="margin: 5px 0; letter-spacing: 3px; color: #fff;">THE ARCHITECT</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="row"><span>Network Size:</span> <span class="highlight">100 Nodes</span></div>
            <div class="row"><span>Monthly Deposit:</span> <span class="gold">₹999 / Head</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="stat-card" style="border-left: 3px solid #00ff00;">
            <div class="row"><span>Total Turnover:</span> <span class="highlight">₹99,900</span></div>
            <div class="row"><span>Your Reward:</span> <span class="gold">₹20,000 / Month</span></div>
        </div>

        <div class="monthly-badge">
            Recurring Revenue Active
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            "जितना बड़ा नेटवर्क, उतना ज्यादा पैसा।" <br>
            STRATEGIC SYSTEM SECURED
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
